      <title>工会表示，致命的船只袭击意味着红海航行需要重新思考</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/deadly-ship-attack-means-red-sea-voyages-need-re-think-nautilus-union-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个主要运输联盟敦促全面停止穿越红海的商船，并在胡塞武装袭击导致三名水手死亡后，进一步呼吁船只重新考虑航行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/deadly-ship-attack-means-red-sea-voyages-need-re-think-nautilus-union-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 12:14:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
